					<![CDATA[
						 <p>No vote from me. The article isn't terrible but it's rather bland. I can see how it fits in with your RI scenario but other than the duplicate showing up it didn't really add much. My biggest problem is the formatting however. I really don't like how the interview logs are clustered in question-answer groups instead of each line being spaced like in every other article.</p> 
				 	]]>
