					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I hadn't read this one before now, but after doing so I must agree. This wouldn't be an issue if the anomalies and plot structures weren't so similar so they could fill different niches, but they really are almost identical and 2054 just has better character interactions for my money.</p> <p>Still looking forward to reading the rest of this team's stuff though, I quite enjoyed the prequel tale to this skip.</p> 
				 	]]>
